title: Camp WeWow Magic Week Day 1: Eyes on the Behind
description:
It's Magic Week at Camp WeWow! Today, we're listening to one of our favorite episodes of Wow in the World, "Eyes on the Behind!" This week, we've got a few tricks up our sleeve with crafts, activities, and games for you, so be sure to check back for more tomorrow! Visit tinkercast.com/camp for directions to our daily activities and challenges. You can share your tinkerings and tales with us at tinkercast.com/share and at 1-888-7WOW-WOW for the chance to be featured at the “campfire” this Friday!
